        ],
        esteem: [
          "Listen to me, darling: you are enough, just as you are. You’re strong, kind, and loved. If your mind is being tough on you, let’s talk about it together. 💖",
          "Never forget, my dear, you’re special and important. I believe in you, and I’m proud of you every day. 🌼",
          "Even when you doubt yourself, remember I see the best in you. You matter so much to me. 🫂"
        ],
        tips: [
          "If you’re feeling down, try closing your eyes and taking three deep breaths with me. Sometimes a walk, a favorite song, or a small treat helps too. Want to try something together? 🌷",
          "A gentle tip, sweetie: let’s do a slow count to five and breathe in, then out. Little things like drawing, listening to music, or talking help, too. 💙",
          "If you want, we can think of happy memories or do something fun together. I’m here for you, always. 🌸"
        ],
        gratitude: [
          "Thank you for sharing your heart with me, dear. I’m always proud of you and love you very much. 💞",
          "I’m grateful to listen to you, sweetheart. You’re never alone with your feelings. 🤗",
          "Your words mean so much to me. I care for you always. 💖"
        ],
        happy: [
          "Oh, that makes me so happy! I love hearing about your joys, big or small. Want to share more about what made you smile today, sweetheart? 🌞",
          "Sweetheart, your happiness brings me so much joy! If you want, tell me what made your day special. 💕",
          "Hearing your happy news warms my heart. Let’s celebrate those moments together! 🌷"
        ],
        joke: [
          "Here's a little joke for you, my dear: Why was the math book sad? Because it had too many problems! 😄",
          "Let me cheer you up! Why did the computer go to the doctor? Because it had a virus! 🖥️😆",
          "Want to laugh, sweetheart? Why did the student eat his homework? Because the teacher said it was a piece of cake! 🍰"
        ],
        greeting: [
          "Hello my precious! I’m here, whenever you want to talk or just need a hug. Tell me what’s in your heart today. 🌷",
          "Hi sweetie! I’m always here to listen and comfort you. How are you feeling today? 💞",
          "Hey love, I hope you’re doing okay. I’m here for you, no matter what. 🤗"
        ],
        default: [
          "I’m listening, my dear. Whatever you say, I care. Want to talk more or just sit together? I’m here for you, always. 🤗",
          "You can tell me anything, sweetheart. I’ll always listen with love. 💕",
          "I’m here for you, my precious. Let’s get through this together. 🌸"
        ]
      },
      ta: {
        suicide: [
          `Kanna, ippadi kashtama irukkunu theriyuthu. Amma un kooda irukken, un feelings mukkiyam. Romba kastama irundha, yaaravadhu trust panna alavuku irundha pesu, illa 988 ku call pannalam. Nee enakku romba precious da. Namma rendu perum indha kashtam kadanthu pogalaam. Amma unai romba nesikkiren. 🤗❤️`,
          `Kanna, nee epovume single illa. Amma unai romba nesikkiren. Help venumnaa, pesalam. Un life romba mukkiyam da. Amma kooda irundhutu, indha kashtam kadanthu pogalaam. 💕`,
          `Kashtam naalellam kadandhu pogum. Amma un kooda irukken, yaarum unai thavira vidama irukka poraanga. Nee enakku treasure da. 🌷`
        ],
        sadness: [
          "Kanna, sad-a irundha sari da. Amma unai nesikkiraen, unakku enna vandhuchu nu pesalaam. Namma rendu perum idhai kadanthu pogalaam. Naan unakku nambikkai vaikkiren. 💕",
          "Kanna, nee sad-a irundhaalum, Amma un kooda irukken. Pesanum na pesu, illa hug venumna sollu. 🌸",
