        ],
        anxiety: [
          "Kanna, deep breath pannu. Amma kooda pesalaam, enna worry pannuthu nu sollu. Amma un kooda irukken, nimmadhiya irukka help pannalaam. 🌸",
          "Anxiety varum, aana Amma unai support pannalaam. Nimmadhiya irukka, Amma kooda breathe pannalaam. 💙",
